'''Esther Lily Nkansah''' yɛ Ghanani mmaranimfo ne kane Soafo a ɔhwɛ Atɔe Mantam no so firi afe 1997 kosi afe 2001 wɔ Rawlings aban ase. Wɔ 2010 mu no, Kane manpanyin Atta Mills bɔɔ ne din kaa Sika Korabea kunini a ene Bank of [[Ghana]] abaguakuo 10 a wɔn botae ne se wɔbeboa ma nhyehyɛ a Ghana mpontuo ‘Better Ghana Agenda no. Owurayere Nkansah san nso yɛ okandifo ma asore kuo a ɛde Dioces wɔ Methodist Asore a ɛwɔ Sekondi.

